Transpop

library(partykit)
library(tidyverse)
transpop <- read.delim("37938-0005-Data.tsv")
transonly <- transpop |>
  filter(GENDER_IDENTITY > 2) |>
  mutate(GENDER_IDENTITY = as.factor(GENDER_IDENTITY)) |>
  select(
    #demographics
    STUDYID,
    GENDER_IDENTITY,
    RACE_RECODE_CAT5,
    SEXMINID,
    AGE,
    WEIGHT_TRANSPOP,
    #trans-specific variables
    INTERNALIZED_I,
    EVERYDAY_I,
    CHILDGNC_I,
    NONDISCLOSURE_I,
    NEGEXPFUTURE_I,
    SOCSUPPORT_I,
    CONNECTEDNESS_I,
    NONAFFIRM_I,
    HCTHREAT_I,
    SOCSUPPORT_SO,
    SOCSUPPORT_FAM,
    SOCSUPPORT_FR,
    #positive health outcomes
    LIFESAT,
    SOCIALWB
  )
